OL,5, The Post Office has apologised for     
OL,6, using racist terms to describe         
OL,7, postmasters wrongly investigated as    
OL,8, part of the Horizon IT scandal.        
OL,10,FAn internal document shows fraud       
OL,11,Finvestigators were asked to group      
OL,12,Fsuspects based on racial features.     
OL,14,FMore than 700 sub-postmasters were     
OL,15,Fprosecuted for false accounting based  
OL,16,Fon information from a flawed system.   
OL,18,FThe scandal has been described as "the 
OL,19,Fmost widespread miscarriage of justice 
OL,20,Fin UK history".                        
